4
00:01:39,379 --> 00:01:42,920
Excuse me, 
 I forgot to recharge my water card.

5
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:45,359
Can I borrow yours?

6
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:49,199
Are we that close?

7
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:53,859
I forgot to introduce myself earlier 
 during the English exercise.

8
00:01:53,859 --> 00:01:58,500
My name is Jiang Qiao Xi. 
 It's nice to meet you.

9
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:02,459
I can't say the same.

10
00:02:02,459 --> 00:02:05,840
Also, I don't easily lend 
 my water card to others.

11
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,739
Why is she treating Jiang Qiao Xi this way?

12
00:02:07,739 --> 00:02:10,080
She has quite a temper.

13
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,999
Jiang Qiao Xi, use mine.

14
00:02:11,999 --> 00:02:13,300
You can use mine as well.

15
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:15,492
There is no need. Thank you.

16
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:29,539
She is new here 
 and not familiar with this place.

17
00:02:29,539 --> 00:02:32,959
Let's greet her with more enthusiasm.

18
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:39,199
Frankly, I've never seen anyone 
 treat Jiang Qiao Xi like this before.

19
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,580
That was too much!

20
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:43,419
Still, he always seems polite.

21
00:02:43,419 --> 00:02:45,060
He wasn't offended.

22
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:47,840
Jiang Qiao Xi is well-mannered.

23
00:02:48,539 --> 00:02:52,960
That's true. 
 But why did she treat him that way?

24
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,539
He only wanted to borrow her water card.

25
00:02:54,539 --> 00:02:57,879
She reacted as if they had a feud.

26
00:02:58,419 --> 00:03:02,279
Maybe that's because she didn't understand

27
00:03:02,279 --> 00:03:04,860
what Jiang Qiao Xi said during English class.

28
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:08,159
He embarrassed her 
 when she had just joined the class.

29
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,960
Exactly! Think about it.

30
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:12,539
She made it to Experimental High School 
 from Qunshan.

31
00:03:12,539 --> 00:03:15,159
She must have been outstanding 
 in her previous class as well,

32
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:17,159
but she came across Jiang Qiao Xi 
 right after she arrived.

33
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:20,580
Her self-esteem must have taken a hit.

34
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:23,900
Teacher He said Jiang Qiao Xi's sentences 
 were above the curriculum level.

35
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:26,419
Most of the students in our class 
 didn't understand them.

36
00:03:26,419 --> 00:03:29,139
I don't think she's angry about this.

37
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:36,080
I think you're the problem.

38
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,439
Me?

39
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,240
Yes! Think about it.

40
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:43,980
You knew nothing about her 
 yet badmouthed her to other students.

41
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:46,460
You are also Jiang Qiao Xi's friend,

42
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:49,500
so she took it out on Jiang Qiao Xi.

43
00:03:50,140 --> 00:03:52,192
What should I do?

44
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:57,479
You should apologize to Lin Qi Le,

45
00:03:57,479 --> 00:04:00,240
but, honestly, it's not your fault.

46
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:03,959
The fault lies with the person 
 who wrote the letter to Jiang Qiao Xi.

47
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:17,079
I heard someone was not tactful

48
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:19,840
and tried to borrow your water card, 
 but you refused.

49
00:04:21,679 --> 00:04:24,420
If I could, I'd even splash water on him.

50
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:27,219
I'll ask him about his intentions.

51
00:04:29,019 --> 00:04:31,239
Who cares?

52
00:04:31,239 --> 00:04:34,639
We don't care about him.

53
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:46,179
Lin Qi Le, someone is looking for you 
 at the fourth-floor stairwell.

54
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:49,459
Who is looking for me?

55
00:04:49,459 --> 00:04:51,920
Go, and you will find out.

56
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,099
Did he say what it's about?

57
00:04:53,099 --> 00:04:56,239
He said he wants to talk to you in person.

58
00:04:56,239 --> 00:04:58,520
Come on, I'll go with you!

59
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:01,160
He is looking for Lin Qi Le.

60
00:05:07,939 --> 00:05:09,752
I'll go alone.

61
00:05:11,919 --> 00:05:15,079
Lin Qi Le, we've met before.

62
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:18,980
It was just before your transfer 
 to the Experimental High School.  Do you remember?

63
00:05:20,036 --> 00:05:21,079
Yes.

64
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:24,720
You made it here 
 with a high score from Qunshan.

65
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,240
Everyone thinks you're awesome.

66
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:31,199
Let's support each other in our studies 
 and grow together.

67
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:36,139
What are you trying to say?

68
00:05:36,139 --> 00:05:38,879
I'm here to apologize.

69
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:41,219
It's my fault. I mistook you for someone else,

70
00:05:41,219 --> 00:05:44,500
and said offensive words to you.

71
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:46,400
I'm sorry.

72
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:54,620
Still, you shouldn't have spoken like that.

73
00:05:54,620 --> 00:06:00,079
Do you really hate us? 
 Especially Jiang Qiao Xi?

74
00:06:02,539 --> 00:06:05,399
The truth is unpleasant, 
 and I don't want to discuss it with you.

75
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:08,899
Lin Qi Le, it's just a misunderstanding.

76
00:06:08,899 --> 00:06:12,932
You are a victim. So is Jiang Qiao Xi.

77
00:06:12,932 --> 00:06:15,699
Don't blame Jiang Qiao Xi. 
 He's outstanding.

78
00:06:15,699 --> 00:06:18,240
- You… 
 - He is a role model in our class.

79
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,600
If you want to blame someone, 
 blame that Cherry

80
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:23,519
who wrote a shameless letter 
 to Jiang Qiao Xi.

81
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:24,860
Enough!

82
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:28,800
You don't know what she wrote. 
 It was disgusting!

83
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:31,639
"Disgusting"?

84
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:33,199
Stop spouting nonsense!

85
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:38,060
Yu Qiao, last time you started a fight, 
 I let it slide.

86
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:40,439
Are you pushing your luck?

87
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,439
What is going on?

88
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:48,540
Did you both dare to be violent toward me?

89
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:51,319
Just wait and see! I'll be in the office.

90
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:53,620
Fei Lin Ge, can't you just talk it over?

91
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:55,820
What's there to talk about?

92
00:06:56,699 --> 00:07:00,060
Oh, no! Oh, no! Our class is in big trouble!

93
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:03,240
It's Lin Qi Le, the new student! 
 She hit someone!

94
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,040
It's true! There was a fight 
 and she hit someone.

95
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:07,819
Go check it out!

96
00:07:09,579 --> 00:07:11,060
Fei Lin Ge has a good relationship 
 with the teachers.

97
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:13,759
It won't be easy for you to explain.

98
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:16,079
What happened?

99
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:20,939
It's all right, I know you well.

100
00:07:20,939 --> 00:07:22,912
I'll defend you.

101
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:25,259
I didn't start a fight!

102
00:07:25,259 --> 00:07:26,639
But you kicked him.

103
00:07:26,639 --> 00:07:28,079
That was self-defense!

104
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:30,440
It was me who started the fight.

105
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,639
He was the first to start cursing.

106
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:35,120
Then he can only blame himself.

107
00:07:36,259 --> 00:07:38,860
It's his fault. 
 He was the one who started it.

108
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:41,439
I believe the teachers here 
 can tell right from wrong.

109
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:43,920
We are not afraid.

110
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,899
Are you both really all right?

111
00:07:45,899 --> 00:07:48,100
With her around, 
 black can be turned into white.

112
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:49,659
You can rest assured.

113
00:07:49,659 --> 00:07:52,500
All right, Fei Lin Ge is mean with his words.

114
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:55,960
Let's be generous and not argue with him.

115
00:07:55,960 --> 00:08:00,020
Class Monitor, you are right. Thank you.

116
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:06,979
What are you looking at? Go back!

117
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:10,459
What should I do? 
 I just arrived and already caused trouble.

118
00:08:10,459 --> 00:08:12,879
It's all right, I'm here.

119
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,959
As for you,

120
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:17,519
not only did I cause trouble, 
 I also implicated you.

121
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:21,540
It makes sense. 
 We did the same thing when we were kids.

122
00:08:31,639 --> 00:08:32,720
Jiang Qiao Xi!

123
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,960
Come with me.

124
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:36,620
- Where are we going? 
 - Take a seat.

125
00:08:44,299 --> 00:08:46,019
Why did they hit you?

126
00:08:46,019 --> 00:08:49,519
I saw Lin Qi Le didn't take you seriously,

127
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:51,200
even though you didn't offend her.

128
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:54,740
I thought maybe it was because 
 I had mistaken her for Cherry earlier.

129
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:57,419
She hates me and resents you, too.

130
00:08:57,419 --> 00:08:58,759
I tried to apologize to her,

131
00:08:58,759 --> 00:09:01,419
but their response was barbaric!

132
00:09:01,419 --> 00:09:04,200
I only said a few words, 
 and then they pushed me!

133
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:07,300
Lin Qi Le even kicked me!

134
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:20,500
Did you curse Cherry 
 when you apologized to them?

135
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:22,179
It's all Cherry's fault!

136
00:09:22,179 --> 00:09:25,039
He wrote such a disgusting letter 
 that annoyed you.

137
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:27,139
Without her, 
 there would be no misunderstandings.

138
00:09:27,139 --> 00:09:29,819
"Disgusting"? Who said it's disgusting?

139
00:09:29,819 --> 00:09:31,120
Isn't it?

140
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:33,056
You!

141
00:09:34,419 --> 00:09:37,992
You called someone disgusting 
 in front of her friends.

142
00:09:37,992 --> 00:09:39,799
If they don't hit you, who will they hit?

143
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:41,720
Jiang Qiao Xi, why are you defending them?

144
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,512
Enough!

145
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:50,220
From now on, stay out of my business.

146
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:52,080
Especially when it involves Lin Qi Le.

147
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:55,800
Lin Qi Le? You and her…

148
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:09,000
We will… become friends.

149
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:12,860
Something's not right.

150
00:10:12,860 --> 00:10:14,799
The teacher hasn't called me yet.

151
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:18,740
That Fei Lin Ge doesn't seem 
 to have taken any action.

152
00:10:18,740 --> 00:10:20,720
They likely find Lynn Cherry too fierce!

153
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:23,779
They thought it over carefully, 
 but they still don't dare challenge you.

154
00:10:23,779 --> 00:10:26,379
It's good to teach him a lesson.

155
00:10:27,020 --> 00:10:29,080
Forget it, I'm new here.

156
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:31,072
It's best if I keep a low profile.

157
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,899
I'll sit here. You sit over there.

158
00:10:41,899 --> 00:10:44,279
I want to watch Cai Fang Yuan's 
 multifunctional player.

159
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:46,659
Why didn't you tell me earlier? 
 I didn't bring it!

160
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:49,799
What did you bring then?

161
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:55,544
Let me check.

162
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,540
All right. I'll just read this.

163
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:04,300
Cherry, are you starting to stray?

164
00:11:05,659 --> 00:11:07,480
I'm just reading.

165
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:11,100
Let me tell you. 
 Strategies printed in books are outdated.

166
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:14,820
Let me tell you how to become 
 a top expert in just three days.

167
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:18,100
After hearing this, I guarantee 
 you'll all be begging me to play games with you.

168
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:19,419
Don't brag about it.

169
00:11:19,419 --> 00:11:21,340
Your strategy is to spend money.

170
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:23,120
What?

171
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,399
Cherry, let me tell you.

172
00:11:25,399 --> 00:11:30,679
World of Warcraft is more than just a game. 
 It has profound significance.

173
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:33,160
Let me tell you about this game. Look!

174
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:37,960
What's on your mind? I'm sitting here. 
 Why won't you talk to me?

175
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:40,840
What's there to talk about?

176
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:44,220
Qin Ye Yun, look at you.

177
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:46,259
We are all from Qun Shan.

178
00:11:46,259 --> 00:11:47,959
Why don't you hang out with us?

179
00:11:47,959 --> 00:11:49,840
You didn't join us 
 at the arcade dance machine.

180
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:52,639
Lin Cherry danced really well.

181
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,999
What is so fun 
 about the arcade dance machine?

182
00:11:59,659 --> 00:12:02,379
Name one. We'll have fun with you.

183
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:10,659
The aquarium. Will you go with me?

184
00:12:11,179 --> 00:12:13,739
Of course, we can go with you.

185
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,380
Lin… Lin Qi Le!

186
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:18,559
Let's go to the aquarium this weekend.

187
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:20,580
The aquarium?

188
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,039
I'm not going.

189
00:12:25,039 --> 00:12:29,059
Still, Qin Ye Yun wants to go. 
 Let's join her.

190
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:37,059
She is upset now. Just agree to it!

191
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:40,810
Okay. Yes, I'll go.

192
00:12:40,810 --> 00:12:42,500
I will go.

193
00:12:46,299 --> 00:12:50,499
Cherry, why don't you want to go 
 to the aquarium?

194
00:13:51,579 --> 00:13:55,720
 Jiang Qiao Xi, look!  
The jellyfishes are so beautiful. 

195
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:58,820
 I really want to take a bite. 
 They must be delicious. 

196
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:02,739
 You can't eat them. 
 Most jellyfish are poisonous. 

197
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:06,620
 How could that be? They're so beautiful. 

198
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:09,220
 The more beautiful they are, 
 the more poisonous they are. 

199
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:11,059
 What are you doing? 

200
00:14:11,059 --> 00:14:13,490
 Oh, no! Jiang Qiao Xi. 

201
00:14:13,490 --> 00:14:15,520
 You've poisoned me! 

202
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:19,560
 Help! Help! 

203
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:25,220
 Cherry, do you want to see jellyfish? 

204
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,540
 Let's go see them together in the future. 

205
00:14:28,319 --> 00:14:31,140
 But there is no aquarium in Qunshan. 

206
00:14:31,140 --> 00:14:33,179
 There is one in the provincial city. 

207
00:14:33,179 --> 00:14:35,700
 I don't like the provincial city. 

208
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,860
 Let's not go then. 

209
00:14:45,899 --> 00:14:48,779
 If you're there, I will like it. 

210
00:14:48,779 --> 00:14:50,944
 We will go then. 

211
00:15:36,419 --> 00:15:37,679
Where are Du Shang and the others?

212
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:40,180
They went to the restroom.

213
00:15:47,179 --> 00:15:49,620
I focused my attention on the fish.

214
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:51,000
My doll was curious.

215
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:54,940
Fish? Aren't they jellyfish?

216
00:15:57,720 --> 00:16:01,630
Cherry, when you look at jellyfish,

217
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:04,200
It doesn't seem 
 as if you're looking at jellyfish.

218
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:08,279
Qin Ye Yun is really something else.

219
00:16:08,279 --> 00:16:11,159
She wanted to visit the aquarium 
 but canceled at the last minute.

220
00:16:11,159 --> 00:16:12,760
You two are just the same.

221
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:16,999
What you say and think 
 can be very confusing.

222
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:20,720
Treat Qin Ye Yun more nicely.

223
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:23,739
Am I not nice to her?

224
00:16:24,299 --> 00:16:25,940
Today, she had something to do 
 and couldn't make it.

225
00:16:25,940 --> 00:16:28,100
You should come with her next time.

226
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:30,239
Why don't you accompany her instead?

227
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:40,860
I have… too many things on my mind.

228
00:16:40,860 --> 00:16:42,744
I have no time.

229
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:04,540
♫  Love is in your eyes  ♫

230
00:17:04,540 --> 00:17:09,120
♫  You will see flowers blooming  ♫

231
00:17:09,120 --> 00:17:09,972
Bye-bye!

232
00:17:09,972 --> 00:17:12,412
♫  Every minute and every second  ♫

233
00:17:12,412 --> 00:17:14,779
♫  I will always be with you  ♫

234
00:17:14,779 --> 00:17:16,920
- It's them again. 
 - Who?

235
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:17,920
What a small world!

236
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:21,652
♫  We soar across the seas  ♫

237
00:17:23,339 --> 00:17:25,336
Don't…

238
00:17:26,816 --> 00:17:27,940
What are you doing?

239
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:30,900
I want to hear what a busy brain sounds like.

240
00:17:30,900 --> 00:17:33,319
Does it sound different 
 from a good watermelon?

241
00:17:33,319 --> 00:17:36,740
That's a watermelon, not a brain.

242
00:17:36,740 --> 00:17:38,359
Did you call me a watermelon 
 just to insult me?

243
00:17:38,359 --> 00:17:40,200
- How could I?" That's impossible. 
 - Come here!

244
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:42,852
I was just joking. 
 Don't take it seriously. It was a joke.

245
00:17:42,852 --> 00:17:45,900
   

246
00:17:52,859 --> 00:17:55,860
Qin Ye Yun! Qin Ye Yun!

247
00:17:55,860 --> 00:17:59,440
Qin Ye Yun from the convenience store.

248
00:18:10,540 --> 00:18:11,860
What's with that expression?

249
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:13,220
What kind of expression should I have 
 while watching TV?

250
00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:15,320
It's not me, it's the TV acting up.

251
00:18:16,499 --> 00:18:19,360
Take a good look at it. 
 I picked it just for you.

252
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:20,700
I'm not giving it to you.

253
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:23,040
Let me take a look.

