- Goodbye, Miss! 
 - Goodbye, Miss!

509
00:39:29,899 --> 00:39:31,639
 Jiang Qiao Xi. 

510
00:39:31,639 --> 00:39:34,760
 Cherry, are you feeling better? 

511
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:37,400
 I want to drink peanut milk, 

512
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:41,680
 but Mom said I can't drink cold beverages 
 when I have a fever or a cold. 

513
00:39:41,680 --> 00:39:43,610
 I can only drink hot water. 

514
00:39:43,619 --> 00:39:47,779
 I don't want to drink hot water. 
 What should I do? 

515
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:56,200
 Don't be afraid! Aunt Juan went to work. 

516
00:39:56,200 --> 00:39:59,680
 I heated up the peanut milk. Drink it! 

517
00:40:06,599 --> 00:40:09,900
 Jiang Qiao Xi, you are so nice. 

518
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:12,300
 I hate being sick the most. 

519
00:40:12,300 --> 00:40:17,239
 From now on, stay with me when I'm sick. 
 Do you understand? 

520
00:40:18,200 --> 00:40:26,500
Jiang Qiao Xi, 
 it's so nice to have you here.

521
00:40:51,340 --> 00:40:53,479
What's wrong? Are you feeling hot?

522
00:40:53,479 --> 00:40:55,492
Why are you here?

523
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:57,820
I'm here to see you.

524
00:40:57,820 --> 00:40:59,400
I don't need you to visit me.

525
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:02,880
Are we that close? 
 There's no need for you to be here.

526
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:08,399
Technically, we are currently classmates.

527
00:41:09,099 --> 00:41:10,579
Thank you, my classmate.

528
00:41:10,579 --> 00:41:12,240
I'm fine now, though.

529
00:41:12,240 --> 00:41:15,999
Don't sit here! It'll be hard to explain 
 if the teacher checks and sees us.

530
00:41:15,999 --> 00:41:17,959
- You should leave. 
 - It's fine.

531
00:41:17,959 --> 00:41:21,419
I'll just say I came to see the doctor 
 and get some medicine!

532
00:41:21,419 --> 00:41:23,900
Weren't you the one 
 who said you couldn't lie?

533
00:41:23,900 --> 00:41:26,400
I can do it if it's for you.

534
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:28,616
Who cares?

535
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:31,500
All right then. I'll shut up.

536
00:41:39,340 --> 00:41:41,779
Leave.

537
00:41:45,500 --> 00:41:50,400
Didn't you just say 
 that it's nice to have me here?

538
00:41:53,660 --> 00:41:56,540
I didn't say that to you.

539
00:41:57,500 --> 00:42:01,800
I remember when you were little,

540
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:05,099
you told me to stay with you 
 whenever you were sick.

541
00:42:05,099 --> 00:42:08,600
Really? I don't remember.

542
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:11,500
It's fine. I'll remember these for you.

543
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:13,604
Jiang Qiao Xi!

544
00:42:17,780 --> 00:42:20,000
Why do you keep repeating these words?

545
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:22,800
Are they the only words in your head?

546
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:24,608
Are you leaving or not?

547
00:42:27,079 --> 00:42:29,120
If you don't, then I will.

548
00:42:31,599 --> 00:42:35,480
I'll leave now. Get a good rest.

549
00:42:36,139 --> 00:42:40,700
D-Don't say those useless words anymore.

550
00:42:40,700 --> 00:42:43,300
I don't like it. I find it annoying.

551
00:42:43,300 --> 00:42:47,000
All right, I got it.

552
00:42:48,300 --> 00:42:51,420
Jiang Qiao Xi, why are you here?

553
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:57,239
- Miss, someone told me not to… 
 - Miss,

554
00:42:57,239 --> 00:43:01,360
he is not feeling well and came to see you,

555
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:03,099
but you weren't here.

556
00:43:03,099 --> 00:43:05,096
Where is the discomfort?

557
00:43:05,096 --> 00:43:08,059
- His head! 
 - His head?

558
00:43:11,320 --> 00:43:15,099
Miss, I just promised someone 
 that I wouldn't lie,

559
00:43:15,099 --> 00:43:16,800
so I'm telling you the truth now.

560
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,700
She and I are in the same class,

561
00:43:18,700 --> 00:43:22,600
and I am here to check on her.

562
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:25,740
Miss, I'm leaving.

